window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Mike Baron delivers a riotous, heartfelt, and ultimately uplifting story in </b><b><i>Florida Man</i></b><b>, brought to life by the inimitable R.C. Bray.</b></p> <p>Gary Duba’s having a bad day. There’s a snake in his toilet, a rabid raccoon in the yard, and his girl Krystal’s in jail for getting naked at a Waffle House and licking the manager.</p> <p>Gary’s a redneck living in a trailer by the swamp. But he’s got dreams, big dreams. Every time he tries to get ahead, fate deals him a low blow. But then he gets lucky...</p> <p>With his best friend, Floyd, Gary sets out to sell his prized Barry Bonds rookie card to raise the $500 needed for bail. But things always find a way of getting out of hand.</p>"; 
